# Coding Standards

## File Organization

### CSS
- Store all CSS in `_includes/common/common.css`
- Maintain centralized styling approach
- Use consistent naming conventions

### JavaScript
- Store all JavaScript in `_includes/common/scripts.js`
- Keep scripts organized and well-commented
- Follow modern JavaScript best practices

## Best Practices
- Maintain separation of concerns
- Ensure cross-browser compatibility
